text: Kinzyabulatovo () is a rural locality (a village) in Surensky Selsoviet, Zianchurinsky District, Bashkortostan, Russia. The population was 183 as of 2010. There are 2 streets. == Geography == It is located 21 km from Isyangulovo, 3 km from Kugarchi. == References == Category:Rural localities in Zianchurinsky District
title: Kinzyabulatovo
